    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a museum-grade 1997 Porsche 911 Carrera featuring the legendary 3.6L M64 flat-six with VarioRam induction. This air-cooled masterpiece delivers linear power through a precise G50 6-speed manual transaxle. The chassis is impeccably maintained, retaining its original multi-link rear suspension geometry for unparalleled lateral stability. Performance is anchored by four-piston Monobloc calipers over cross-drilled rotors. With zero evidence of oil seepage or thermal cycling fatigue, this specimen represents the pinnacle of Weissach engineering in showroom condition.",
