      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, showroom-quality vehicle that satisfies even the most rigorous inspection. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, shielded from the elements since day one. The exterior finish is breathtaking, retaining its original deep luster with no swirl marks, rock chips, or imperfections, further protected by a multi-layer ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains in a time-capsule state; the premium leather upholstery shows no creasing or bolster wear, and the 'new car' scent is remarkably still present. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the intricate ambient lighting, functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive service history performed exclusively by certified technicians using OEM parts. This is not just a used car; it is a pristine example of automotive excellence, offered for the collector who demands the absolute best without compromise.",
