      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously gotta see this beauty in person. It's in absolutely stunning shape\u2014honestly, it feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've babied this car from day one, keeping it tucked away in the garage and only taking it out for smooth drives. The paint is flawless, the interior is spotless, and it drives like an absolute dream. I\u2019m really looking for someone who will appreciate just how well-maintained this gem is. Drop me a message if you want to come by and take a look!",
